detaileddescription.para: Return the maximum bitrate in bits / sec contained in the packet.

Process an incoming report block to compute loss rate percentage. It tries to compute loss rate, depending on the previous report block. It may fails if the two reports are too close or if a discontinuity occurred. You should NOT use loss rate field of the report block directly (see below). This estimator is useful for two reasons: first, on AVPF session, multiple reports can be received in a short period and loss_rate contained in these reports is unreliable. Secondly, it computes the loss rate using the cumulative loss factor which allows us to take into consideration duplicates packets as well.
